Node.Notes: Sense seems to be that this "speech" and "knowledge" given comes without audible voice.
Uncertain what "line/cord" would mean here. Many go with "voice" (often positing that the consonant lamed was accidentally omitted, with the addition of which the word "voice" is formed).
Arrogant ones, which could refer to arrogant people, but probably willful sins in light of rest of verse.
